&lt;p&gt;Note that, matrix multiplied by its pseudo-inverse doesn&#39;t give the identity matrix.&lt;br /&gt;
 注意，一个矩阵和它的伪逆矩阵相乘，结果不为单位矩阵。&lt;/p&gt;
