\frac{\partial}{\partial\theta}J(\theta)
&amp;amp;=\frac12\frac{\partial}{\partial\theta}(\theta^T{\rm X}^T-y^T)({\rm X}\theta-y)\\
&amp;amp;=\frac12\frac{\partial}{\partial\theta}(\theta^T{\rm X}^T{\rm X}\theta-\theta^T{\rm X}^Ty-y^T{\rm X}\theta+y^Ty)\\
&amp;amp;={\rm X}^T{\rm X}\theta-{\rm X}^Ty
