&lt;p&gt;As with affine sets, it can be shown that a set is convex if and only if it contains every convex combination of its points.&lt;br /&gt;
 和仿射集类似，一个集合是凸集当且仅当这个集合包含其中任意点的所有凸组合。&lt;/p&gt;
