&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;image-20221004200401526.png&#34; alt=&#34;image-20221004200401526&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The idea of a convex combination can be generalized to include infinite sums, integrals, and, in the most general form, probability distributions.&lt;br /&gt;
 凸组合的概念可以扩展到无穷级数、积分以及大多数形式的概率分布。&lt;/p&gt;
