x^TAx &amp;amp;= \frac12x^TAx+\frac12x^TAx\\
&amp;amp;= \textcolor{red}{\frac12x^TAx+\frac12(x^TAx)^T}\\
&amp;amp;= \frac12x^TAx+\frac12x^TA^Tx\\
&amp;amp;= x^T(\frac12A+\frac12A^T)x
\end{aligned}
