 &lt;h1 id=&#34;mathematical-optimization-数学优化问题&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#mathematical-optimization-数学优化问题&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Mathematical Optimization 数学优化问题&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;definition-定义&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#definition-定义&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Definition 定义&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A mathematical optimization problem, or just optimization problem, has the form：&lt;br /&gt;
数学优化问题，也称最优化问题，有如下的形式：&lt;/p&gt;
\begin{equation}\tag{1.1} \label{eq1.1}
    \begin{aligned}
        &amp; {\rm minimize}\quad f_0(x) \\
        &amp; {\rm subject~to}\quad f_i(x) \le b_i~(i = 1,\cdots, m)
    \end{aligned}
\end{equation}

&lt;ul&gt;
