&lt;h3 id=&#34;solving-least-squares-problems-求解最小二乘问题&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#solving-least-squares-problems-求解最小二乘问题&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; solving least-squares problems 求解最小二乘问题&lt;/h3&gt;
